Sentencas: Thin film growth of yttria stabilized zirconia (YSZ) using atmospheric aerosol assisted chemical vapor deposition (AA-CVD) from beta-diketonates is studied.
Titulo: Thin film growth of yttria stabilized zirconia by aerosol assisted chemical vapor deposition

Sentencas: The influence of nature and concentration of metal precursors and solvents on thin film growth, microstructure and composition is investigated as a function of deposition temperature.
Titulo: Thin film growth of yttria stabilized zirconia by aerosol assisted chemical vapor deposition

Sentencas: AA-CVD is able to produce smooth and homogeneous YSZ thin films of controlled thickness and stoichiometry.
Titulo: Thin film growth of yttria stabilized zirconia by aerosol assisted chemical vapor deposition

Sentencas: Amorphous, nanocrystalline or columnar microstructures can be obtained at deposition temperatures between 300 and 650 degrees C.
Titulo: Thin film growth of yttria stabilized zirconia by aerosol assisted chemical vapor deposition

Sentencas: In the same temperature regime, a transition from surface reaction to diffusion controlled film growth is observed.
Titulo: Thin film growth of yttria stabilized zirconia by aerosol assisted chemical vapor deposition

Sentencas: For applications as gas separating membranes, e.g. for micro-solid oxide fuel cell electrolytes, randomly oriented nanocrystalline microstructures with grain sizes in the range of 10 nm are promising.
Titulo: Thin film growth of yttria stabilized zirconia by aerosol assisted chemical vapor deposition
